title: Michelle Wolf And Amber Ruffin: Late Night Trivia Fight
description: Comedian Michelle Wolf opens up about her performance at the White House Correspondents' dinner, and Amber Ruffin talks about writing for Late Night With Seth Meyers. Then, they go head to head in not one, but two games!
